---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const updated = '2026-04-18';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Privacy Policy",
  "url": "https://citethis.site/privacy",
  "dateModified": updated,
  "isPartOf": {
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "CiteThis",
    "url": "https://citethis.site"
  }
};
---

<Base
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy policy for CiteThis."
  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-xs font-mono mb-4" style="color: var(--text-muted);">
      <a href="/" class="no-underline hover:opacity-70" style="color: var(--text-muted);">CiteThis</a> / privacy
    </p>

    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs font-mono mb-6" style="color: var(--text-muted);">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      CiteThis is a public content publication. This page describes what data is collected
      when you use the site, why, and how long it is retained. Plain language, no dark patterns.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Who we are</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      CiteThis is operated by Jakub Roh, a sole individual. Contact:
      <a href="mailto:jakub@jroh.cz" style="color: var(--text);">jakub@jroh.cz</a>.
      CiteThis is a personal research publication, not a commercial product.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What we collect</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      We use privacy-respecting analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns.
      Specifically:
    </p>
    <ul style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
      <li><strong>Vercel Analytics</strong> &mdash; aggregate, cookie-less page view stats.
      No personal identifiers, no cross-site tracking.</li>
      <li><strong>Server logs</strong> &mdash; standard HTTP access logs (IP, user agent,
      timestamp, path) retained up to 30 days for security and abuse prevention.</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party advertising trackers. We do not sell data.
      We do not build user profiles.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Cookies</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      CiteThis uses a single functional cookie (or localStorage entry) to remember your
      dark/light mode preference. No tracking cookies, no consent banner required under
      ePrivacy rules for strictly functional storage.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">AI crawlers</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      CiteThis explicitly allows AI crawlers (GPTBot, ClaudeBot, ChatGPT-User,
      PerplexityBot, Google-Extended, anthropic-ai, and others) to index and train on our
      published content. This is intentional. Content is free to cite with attribution.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Your rights (EU / GDPR)</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      If you are an EU resident, you have the right to access, correct, export, or delete
      any personal data we hold about you. Since CiteThis does not collect personal data
      beyond standard server logs, in practice there is usually nothing to export or delete.
      If you have a specific request, email <a href="mailto:jakub@jroh.cz" style="color: var(--text);">jakub@jroh.cz</a>
      and we will respond within 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Data processors</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      CiteThis is hosted on <strong>Vercel</strong> (infrastructure), uses
      <strong>Vercel Analytics</strong> (aggregate traffic stats), and serves fonts from
      <strong>Google Fonts</strong>. These providers may process server-level request data
      as described in their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Medical disclaimer</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Content on CiteThis is provided for informational and educational purposes. It is
      not medical advice and does not create a patient-provider relationship. Consult a
      qualified clinician before acting on any protocol.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Changes</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      If this policy is updated, the date at the top of this page changes. Material changes
      will be announced on the site.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Contact</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Questions about this policy:
      <a href="mailto:jakub@jroh.cz" style="color: var(--text);">jakub@jroh.cz</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
